'From Squeak3.1alpha of 6 February 2001 [latest update: #4173] on 18 August 2001 at 11:29:35 am'!"Change Set:		BlueMPEGFileDialog-kfrDate:			11 August 2001Author:			Karl Ramberg Better file dialog for MPEGMoviePlayerMorph (the blue one)"!!MPEGDisplayMorph methodsFor: 'file open/close' stamp: 'kfr 8/11/2001 09:03'!openMPEGFile	"Invoked by the 'Open' button. Prompt for a file name and try to open that file as an MPEG file."	| result |	result _ (FileList2 modalFileSelectorForSuffixes: #('mp3' 'mpg' 'mpeg')) .	result ifNil: [^ self].	self stopPlaying.	self openFileNamed: (result fullName).! !